descriptionNullable: This data is collected from the monthly published passengers statistics on Heathrow website. It includes total passengers for domestic and international for all airports excluding Gatwick, Stansted, Edinburgh, Naples, Aberdeen, Glasgow and Southampton. Some simple calendar columns are added such as year, month, number of weekdays, and number of weekends to facilitate some analysis.
title: UK Air Travel Passengers
subtitle: Monthly traffic statistics Jan'05 - Jun'22
description: This data is collected from the monthly published passengers statistics on Heathrow website. It includes total passengers for domestic and international for all airports excluding Gatwick, Stansted, Edinburgh, Naples, Aberdeen, Glasgow and Southampton. Some simple calendar columns are added such as year, month, number of weekdays, and number of weekends to facilitate some analysis.
